cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.NE 

The paper deals with the application of deep convolutional neural networks for automatic segmentation of liver and its tumors on CT images. This falls under the domain of computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI). The use of histogram equalization for enhancing the segmented liver region suggests the involvement of multimedia (cs.MM) techniques. Additionally, the use of Jaccard distance as a loss function indicates the use of optimization techniques commonly used in neural networks (cs.NE).
